body_text:
Does it give sone kind of error message?
…
On Mon, 5 Mar 2018, 15:37 VincentLin78, ***@***.***> wrote:
 I built it using bazel and got a 5.1MB TfLiteCameraDemo.apk, but it can't
 be installed. The console just got stuck as executing the "adb install ..."
 Your pre-build one is 23.1MB and can be installed without any problem.

 My environment

 Android Studio 3.2 Canary 4(android virtual device : Pixel 2 XL API 27)
 bazel 0.11.0
 tensorflow master(no custom modification)
 stand-alone ndk-r14b, sdk within android-studio 3..2
 MacOS High Sierra 10.13.3

 My step

 bazel build --cxxopt=--std=c++11
 //tensorflow/contrib/lite/java/demo/app/src/main:TfLiteCameraDemo
 --config=android_arm64 --cpu=arm64-v8a --fat_apk_cpu=arm64-v8a

 adb install -r
 bazel-bin/tensorflow/contrib/lite/java/demo/app/src/main/TfLiteCameraDemo.apk

 —
